contract_type.reasoning: The agreement's title and the body describe Licensor granting Licensee rights to reproduce, display, transmit and distribute "Licensed Content" on the Licensee Site and Related Media, and includes license fees and royalties. The primary subject matter is granting IP/content usage rights — i.e., a license of content and trademarks.

notice_period.raw_snippet: Thereafter, this Agreement shall renew automatically for one (1) additional three (3) year period (the "Renewal Term" and collectively, together with the Initial Term, the "Term") unless either party provides the other with written notice of non-renewal at least ninety (90) days before the expiration of the Initial Term].
notice_period.reasoning: Section 6.1 contains the auto-renewal clause and specifies the advance written notice required to prevent automatic renewal: "at least ninety (90) days before the expiration of the Initial Term." This is the notice to prevent renewal, as requested.

expiration_date.raw_snippet: The initial term of this Agreement commences as of the Effective Date and, unless terminated earlier pursuant to any express provision of this Agreement, shall continue until five (5) years following the Effective Date (the "Initial Term").
expiration_date.reasoning: Section 6.1 defines the Initial Term as continuing "until five (5) years following the Effective Date." This is a relative term specifying the contract duration rather than a calendar date.
expiration_date.normalized_value: five (5) years following the Effective Date

renewal_term.raw_snippet: Thereafter, this Agreement shall renew automatically for one (1) additional three (3) year period (the "Renewal Term" and collectively, together with the Initial Term, the "Term") unless either party provides the other with written notice of non-renewal at least ninety (90) days before the expiration of the Initial Term].
renewal_term.reasoning: This sentence in Section 6.1 describes the renewal: an automatic renewal for one additional three-year period (the Renewal Term).
renewal_term.normalized_value: One (1) additional three (3) year automatic renewal
